snippet.title: Amber Mark - What It Is (Visualiser)
snippet.description:
My debut album Three Dimensions Deep will be out on January 28, 2022. Pre-order now: https://ambermark.lnk.to/ThreeDimensionsDeepID
Tickets to my 2022 world tour are on sale now: https://www.ambermarkmusic.com/

Three Dimensions deep is a musical journey of what questions you begin to ask yourself when you start looking to the universe for answers. I can only go as deep as the third dimension as that’s how we see the world but what about when you start looking to the universe within for answers.

Sign up to my mailing list to be the first to hear about new releases and upcoming live dates: https://AmberMark.lnk.to/SignUpID 
 
Follow 
Instagram: https://AmberMark.lnk.to/InstagramID 
Spotify: https://AmberMark.lnk.to/SpotifyID 
Twitter: https://AmberMark.lnk.to/TwitterID 
Tik Tok: https://AmberMark.lnk.to/TikTokID 
Facebook: https://AmberMark.lnk.to/FacebookID

Lyrics:
I gave it my all  
I tried  
But nothing could stop this fire  
So hard to leave it all behind  

And I know   
The good with the bad  
N we fall  
But what is the point of it all   

So there goes my heart  
I fell apart  
Trying to love  
Wanna be free 
So God tell me please  
Is it in the stars  
Oh    

Feel it in my bones  
Oh I gotta know  
Tell me what it is  
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is 
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is 

On my mind always   
At least 3 times a day   
Tell me what it is   
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is  
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is
 
Is it that sense of wonder  
(Wonder) 
It hit like lightening  
(Lightening) 
Feel that inner thunder  
(Thunder)  
It’s so inviting  
(Oooh)  

Feel it in my bones  
Oh I gotta know  
Tell me what it is  
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is 
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is     

Dive deep in the dark  
With no light  
And I’m looking for a sign  
Should I have left it all behind  
And I know  
Life really takes its toll  
But what is the point of it all  
Yeah     

So there goes my heart  
I fell apart  
Trying to love  
Wanna be free 
So God tell me please  
Is it in the stars  
Oh    

Feel it in my bones  
Oh I gotta know  
Tell me what it is 
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is 
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is 

On my mind always   
At least 3 times a day   
Tell me what it is   
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is  
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is  

Is it that sense of wonder 
(Wonder) 
It hit like lightening  
(Lightening) 
Feel that inner thunder  
(Thunder)  
It’s so inviting  
(Oooh)  

Feel it in my bones  
Oh I gotta know  
Tell me what it is  
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is 
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is 
 
Don’t know how  
A feeling so strange  
The way time never stays the same  
So is life with failure and age  
Wondering why do we throw so much shame  
You and I are one in the same  
Dust from a heart to a flame 
Is it love that through proves in our faith  
Or how we move spiralling

Feel it in my bones  
Oh I gotta know  
Tell me what it is  
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is 
(What it is what it is what it is)  
It is
